%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=96c76579\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"276c73668a431dffc84006695afc10a5b7db8d98","tid":1777872,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edff3eac052285847375228c9b8773fdfebb96e2","tid":1777872,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"密碼送你餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"燈神話林鄭唔會落台 <br />\n香港無雙普選兼燈神萬歲<br />\n兼牙齒當金洗<br />\n<br />\n佢間鋪唔係用平料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed3960a4aabe658dffdfc05333a79e67de3879b","tid":1777872,"uid":200495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"燒山好野"},{"pid":"d19b7e2a211dd8f9b79422138b6aa830d60277a7","tid":1777872,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"燒山間堅石燒味道如何? 想幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db21af82cf6ce0ca0fabb844b1bc403034c0c92","tid":1777872,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d19b7e2a211dd8f9b79422138b6aa830d60277a7","tid":1777872,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"r